{"tid":803412,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馮盈盈好奇蛋蛋受傷有幾痛？麥明詩：做親密行為都會整親","createTime":"2018-09-02T09:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T11:37:07.000Z","uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8b392eef8ed3a4232a70fd424e986dcf8c9defdd","tid":803412,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】麥明詩與馮盈盈兩個智慧與美貌並重的冠軍港姐，但她們有份主持的節目《＃後生仔傾吓偈》內容，被指尺度愈來愈高，就以之前有集講「後生女最葡萄男仔乜野？」，麥明詩一開口即說：「唔使M痛！唔使換衛生巾！」馮盈盈就話：「唔使大肚，唔使有橙皮紋，唔使陰道鬆馳啦。」<br />\n<br />\n然後盈盈還好奇問：「我想問你哋俾人打嗰粒蛋蛋係咪好痛㗎？」其中一位男生話未試過中蛋蛋，麥明詩也不相信說：「有時做啲好親密行為都會整親㗎嘛！」不過網民覺得這節目最難頂，是一班嘉賓同主持疊住發表意見，「好吵啊。一個一個說嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9B%88%E7%9B%88%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%87%E8%9B%8B%E8%9B%8B%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E7%97%9B-%E9%BA%A5%E6%98%8E%E8%A9%A9-%E5%81%9A%E8%A6%AA%E5%AF%86%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E6%95%B4%E8%A6%AA-070200970.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259B%2588%25E7%259B%2588%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%259B%258B%25E8%259B%258B%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E7%2597%259B-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25A9%25A9-%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AF%2586%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2595%25B4%25E8%25A6%25AA-070200970.html&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=960b0fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9B%88%E7%9B%88%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%87%E8%9B%8B%E8%9B%8B%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E7%97%9B-%E9%BA%A5%E6%98%8E%E8%A9%A9-%E5%81%9A%E8%A6%AA%E5%AF%86%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E6%95%B4%E8%A6%AA-070200970.html</a>"},{"pid":"958663d25a2f4a5701338fa83abc248e75482277","tid":803412,"uid":894,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"講得多依啲野就變煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3e4ca5cfcd05